{"tid":565944,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有種人話自己好真 其實好撚假","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T16:15:48.000Z","uid":144559,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ab06961112f67bcc51672d06eccb6b0d74b8720d","tid":565944,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"唔知有冇人明<br />\n<br />\n話說我之前fd搭fd識左個女仔 大我三年 22歲到啦<br />\n一開始覺得佢份人幾nice<br />\n但識下識下發現佢只係表面<br />\n喺ig snapchat係咁話<br />\n「我係咁直接架啦」「我份人就比較真。。」etc<br />\n佢對對個個都表面nice 令你以爲自己同佢好fd<br />\n實際上佢揀人嚟對佢好 <br />\n但奇怪既係<br />\n佢可以為左識左一日嘅朋友 <br />\n煲湯燙茶買禮物<br />\n即刻飛的搵佢<br />\n呢啲事只係發生識左之後嘅兩三日<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔只係一個 係幾個<br />\n可以即刻喺ig post相<br />\n話「最喜歡xx」「大愛xx」「冇你都唔知點算」<br />\n我同個fd呆撚咗 識得嗰一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我開始懷疑佢係咪les<br />\n不過講翻轉頭<br />\n我一開始當佢真心fd 點知發現佢係世界fd<br />\n當我覺得應該同佢唔夾<br />\n佢又搵我傾偈<br />\n唔想同我fd就咪痴埋黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一陣佢比人話幾句<br />\n就話我份人係咁真架啦<br />\n<br />\n利申絲打嚟"},{"pid":"aa4d74d3f5ff22c281a22b4c0e3e5051daec2a62","tid":565944,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:56:30.000Z","msg":"自己仲要好撚傻 真係當正佢真心朋友而執著好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f7b8cac6415b425ee90901bb492b21fa859738","tid":565944,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"sheshe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb00451f97c3eebd9a9ae921dbb619d6793ec6dc","tid":565944,"uid":144559,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7f7b8cac6415b425ee90901bb492b21fa859738","tid":565944,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"sheshe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"佢係les既話我就原諒佢 但有啲女仔有男朋友佢都可以係咁"},